d(x,C) = \inf_{c \in C} d(x,c).
A
F_n = \{x \in X \mid d(x, X \setminus A) \geq \frac1n\}
F_n \subseteq F_{n+1} \subseteq A
A = \bigcup_{n=1}^{\infty} F_n
0 \leq f_n \leq 1
I_A
f_n \to I_A
P
f_n(x) = 0
x \in X \setminus A
f_n(x) = 1
x \in F_n
 f_n(x) = \frac{d(x,X\setminus A)}{d(x,X \setminus A)+d(x,F_n)} 
